This is a port of Quake3 to run on 2727 via the USB hostport, based on the
ioq3 codebase. All 2727-specific modifications are enclosed by one of

VCMODS_MISC - small miscellaneous changes
VCMODS_OPENGLES - remove desktop GL dependencies
VCMODS_DEPTH - remove depth buffer clears
VCMODS_NOSDL - remove SDL dependencies

You will need to put valid pak and license files in 

misc/msvc/baseq3

and copy the file q3config.cfg into 

/Documents and Settings/<user>/Application Data/Quake3/baseq3